title: Cave Story soundtrack m4a
description:
Cave Story soundtrack in m4a
There's few tracks you won't hear in the game because the was written but wasn't included.

The source of music is a Tribute site cavestory.org
The difference is I've thrown away duplicates with midi effects you won't hear in the original game, added track numbers. Plus I included lovingly handcrafted cover art with Quote and Curly riding Balrog, game name in japanese and Studio Pixel logo, wich was always missing )
So you can finally play anywhere now and enjoy tracks in the right order
